name: Freddy Vences
bio: Freddy Vences, a full-stack developer with a passion for problem-solving, helping others, self improvement and can't forget, tech! Proficient in HTML5, JavaScript, CSS3, jQuery, while actively taking on new skills and computer languages. Backed by over 11 years of experience working in teams, customer service, data entry, and financial services. Detail-oriented self-starter, well-organized, efficient, able to work independently or in a group setting. A truly dependable professional with dynamic communication skills eager to contribute to company success.
